          "level": 2,
          "text": "Discussion",
          "type": "heading"
        },
        {
          "type": "paragraph",
          "inlineContent": [
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": "If your container view controller derives the hidden state of the status bar from one of its child view controllers, implement this method to specify which child view controller you want to control the hidden/unhidden state. If you return "
            },
            {
              "type": "codeVoice",
              "code": "nil"
            },
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": " or do not override this method, the status bar hidden/unhidden state for "
            },
            {
              "type": "codeVoice",
              "code": "self"
            },
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": " is used. "
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "type": "paragraph",
          "inlineContent": [
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": "If you change the return value from this method, call the "
            },
